  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 06/06/2022 at 11:30pm CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.18.7-MinorChanges\">Minor Changes</h3><ul><li><p>Added support for manually accepting cards with Square.</p><ul><li><p>Locations can now key in card payments manually, such as when accepting a payment from a customer over the phone.</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Made some minor improvements to our in-app help tool.</p></li></ul><h3 id=\"id-1.18.7-BugFixes\">Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Resolved a &quot;This Site Can't Be Reached&quot; error sometimes appearing in the Inventory Count process.</p></li><li><p>Automated Notifications, which were experiencing delayed sendings or which stopped sending in some instances, now send on time again.</p></li></ul>",
